<p>Here is the math. A cleaning company spending $500 per month on SEO that generates 20 qualified leads per month has a cost per lead of $25. If 8 of those leads book recurring weekly cleanings at $150 per visit, that is $4,800 per month in recurring revenue from $500 in marketing. The customer lifetime value of a weekly cleaning client is $7,800 per year. One good SEO campaign pays for itself many times over.</p>
